{
  "markdown": "<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><body><div id=\"__next\"><div><div><div class=\"fbf608df\" id=\"site_header_placeholder\"></div><section class=\"d24b69b6\"><div><div class=\"fdf7fc2f\"><div class=\"b8f4df87\"><button class=\"f8d00a9a\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"currentColor\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M6.99118 9.00883C5.28238 7.30003 5.28238 4.51947 6.99118 2.81029C8.69997 1.1015 11.4805 1.1015 13.1897 2.81029C14.8985 4.51947 14.8985 7.30003 13.1893 9.00883C11.4805 10.7176 8.69997 10.7176 6.99118 9.00883ZM14.271 10.0902C16.5763 7.78487 16.5763 4.03425 14.271 1.72896C11.9658 -0.576321 8.21475 -0.576321 5.90946 1.72896C3.88178 3.75665 3.63974 6.90161 5.17914 9.19886L0 14.3776L1.62238 16L6.80114 10.8209C9.09839 12.3603 12.2434 12.1178 14.271 10.0902Z\"></path></svg></button><input type=\"search\" enterkeyhint=\"search\" placeholder=\"What can we help you find...\" class=\"e68f22d3\" value=\"xyzzyplugh9876543210abcdef\"><button class=\"b87a0a27\">✕</button></div><button data-testid=\"followup-button\" class=\"c8a34de1\"><svg class=\"ab31ec50\" width=\"11\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 11 12\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g id=\"Arrow\"><path id=\"Arrow_2\" d=\"M6.375 12L5.57306 11.1981L8.34525 8.4375H0V0H1.125V7.3125H8.34525L5.57306 4.54031L6.36338 3.73856L10.5 7.875L6.375 12Z\" fill=\"black\"></path></g></svg>Ask a follow-up</button></div><div><div class=\"f19602ae\" data-testid=\"answer-block\"><div class=\"abc61b22\"><span class=\"c8f81869\">BETA</span>Our AI tool summarized this answer from Wirecutter’s published reporting. This technology is still in development. Please review citations for more information.</div><div><div class=\"f2e92708\"><div class=\"f2e92708\">We recommend using remote-specific job boards to find remote work.<span class=\"dc76029c\"><a class=\"cdfc14ba\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" data-gtm-trigger=\"click_tracking\" data-event-trigger=\"click\" data-event-data-type=\"click\" data-event-data-trigger=\"module\" data-module-name=\"search_click\" data-module-context=\"summary_citation\" data-module-post_id=\"177746\" data-module-url=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" data-module-index=\"1\"><span class=\"ef2e77f0\">1</span></a></span></div><div class=\"f2e92708\">Sites like Working Nomads and We Work Remotely list many remote job openings, often categorized by skill or employment type.<span class=\"dc76029c\"><a class=\"cdfc14ba\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" data-gtm-trigger=\"click_tracking\" data-event-trigger=\"click\" data-event-data-type=\"click\" data-event-data-trigger=\"module\" data-module-name=\"search_click\" data-module-context=\"summary_citation\" data-module-post_id=\"177746\" data-module-url=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" data-module-index=\"1\"><span class=\"ef2e77f0\">1</span></a></span></div><div class=\"f2e92708\">Working Nomads currently has over 20,000 openings, with many in software development.<span class=\"dc76029c\"><a class=\"cdfc14ba\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" data-gtm-trigger=\"click_tracking\" data-event-trigger=\"click\" data-event-data-type=\"click\" data-event-data-trigger=\"module\" data-module-name=\"search_click\" data-module-context=\"summary_citation\" data-module-post_id=\"177746\" data-module-url=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" data-module-index=\"1\"><span class=\"ef2e77f0\">1</span></a></span></div><div class=\"f2e92708\">We Work Remotely also features jobs in design, copywriting, and other fields.<span class=\"dc76029c\"><a class=\"cdfc14ba\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" data-gtm-trigger=\"click_tracking\" data-event-trigger=\"click\" data-event-data-type=\"click\" data-event-data-trigger=\"module\" data-module-name=\"search_click\" data-module-context=\"summary_citation\" data-module-post_id=\"177746\" data-module-url=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" data-module-index=\"1\"><span class=\"ef2e77f0\">1</span></a></span></div><div class=\"f2e92708\">Another option is Jobspresso, which handpicks opportunities and currently lists over 1,000 jobs.<span class=\"dc76029c\"><a class=\"cdfc14ba\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" data-gtm-trigger=\"click_tracking\" data-event-trigger=\"click\" data-event-data-type=\"click\" data-event-data-trigger=\"module\" data-module-name=\"search_click\" data-module-context=\"summary_citation\" data-module-post_id=\"177746\" data-module-url=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" data-module-index=\"1\"><span class=\"ef2e77f0\">1</span></a></span></div><div class=\"f2e92708\">For higher-paying roles, consider Ladders, which features remote jobs paying $100,000 or more.<span class=\"dc76029c\"><a class=\"cdfc14ba\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" data-gtm-trigger=\"click_tracking\" data-event-trigger=\"click\" data-event-data-type=\"click\" data-event-data-trigger=\"module\" data-module-name=\"search_click\" data-module-context=\"summary_citation\" data-module-post_id=\"177746\" data-module-url=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" data-module-index=\"1\"><span class=\"ef2e77f0\">1</span></a></span></div><div class=\"f2e92708\">Some sites, like FlexJobs, also offer part-time and freelance remote work.<span class=\"dc76029c\"><a class=\"cdfc14ba\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" data-gtm-trigger=\"click_tracking\" data-event-trigger=\"click\" data-event-data-type=\"click\" data-event-data-trigger=\"module\" data-module-name=\"search_click\" data-module-context=\"summary_citation\" data-module-post_id=\"177746\" data-module-url=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" data-module-index=\"1\"><span class=\"ef2e77f0\">1</span></a></span></div><div class=\"f2e92708\">Remember to highlight freelance or business experience on your resume.<span class=\"dc76029c\"><a class=\"cdfc14ba\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" data-gtm-trigger=\"click_tracking\" data-event-trigger=\"click\" data-event-data-type=\"click\" data-event-data-trigger=\"module\" data-module-name=\"search_click\" data-module-context=\"summary_citation\" data-module-post_id=\"177746\" data-module-url=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" data-module-index=\"1\"><span class=\"ef2e77f0\">1</span></a></span></div><div class=\"f2e92708\">When interviewing, emphasize transparency, communication, autonomy, and self-awareness.<span class=\"dc76029c\"><a class=\"cdfc14ba\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" data-gtm-trigger=\"click_tracking\" data-event-trigger=\"click\" data-event-data-type=\"click\" data-event-data-trigger=\"module\" data-module-name=\"search_click\" data-module-context=\"summary_citation\" data-module-post_id=\"177746\" data-module-url=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" data-module-index=\"1\"><span class=\"ef2e77f0\">1</span></a></span></div></div><div class=\"e918844b\"><ul><li><span class=\"ef2e77f0\">1</span><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" data-gtm-trigger=\"click_tracking\" data-event-trigger=\"click\" data-event-data-type=\"click\" data-event-data-trigger=\"module\" data-module-name=\"search_click\" data-module-context=\"citation\" data-module-post_id=\"177746\" data-module-url=\"https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/blog/how-to-get-hired-for-a-remote-job/\" data-module-index=\"1\">How to Get Hired for a Remote Job</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"bb903e3f\"><div class=\"a74945b8\"><p>I found this answer helpful</p><span data-testid=\"thumbs-up\" data-gtm-trigger=\"click_tracking\" data-event-trigger=\"click\" data-event-data-type=\"click\" data-event-data-trigger=\"module\" data-module-name=\"search_feedback\" data-module-context=\"I found this answer helpful\" data-module-label=\"yes\"><svg class=\"bd409c01\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 13\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M10.8947 12.0944H3.47383V4.61864L8.11881 0L8.38794 0.0992238C8.57177 0.226424 8.71251 0.385 8.81015 0.574952C8.90767 0.764903 8.93378 0.962274 8.88847 1.16706L8.87148 1.1866L8.25201 4.61864H12.9074C13.208 4.61864 13.4652 4.72562 13.6791 4.93959C13.893 5.15344 14 5.41067 14 5.71129V6.41825C14 6.50015 13.9937 6.57354 13.981 6.63845C13.9684 6.70335 13.9451 6.77114 13.9111 6.84182L11.9795 11.3894C11.8828 11.605 11.7368 11.7764 11.5417 11.9036C11.3465 12.0308 11.1308 12.0944 10.8947 12.0944ZM4.35733 11.2109H10.8947C10.9426 11.2109 10.9916 11.1978 11.0417 11.1716C11.0918 11.1455 11.13 11.1019 11.1562 11.041L13.1165 6.47058V5.71129C13.1165 5.65024 13.0969 5.60011 13.0577 5.56092C13.0185 5.52173 12.9684 5.50214 12.9074 5.50214H7.20133L7.96845 1.38658L4.35733 4.98461V11.2109ZM3.47383 4.61864V5.50214H0.883495V11.2109H3.47383V12.0944H0V4.61864H3.47383Z\" fill=\"black\"></path></svg></span><span data-testid=\"thumbs-down\" data-gtm-trigge